Package net.minecraftforge.fml.network

Class FMLLoginWrapper

java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.fml.network.FMLLoginWrapper
public class FMLLoginWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
Wrapper for custom login packets. Transforms unnamed login channel messages into channels dispatched the same as regular custom packets.
